cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-categories, as it deals with generating multi-sentence descriptions for videos. The use of adversarial techniques also suggests that it could fall under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the evaluation on the ActivityNet Captions dataset indicates that it could also be relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
